Given I have opened the ebay website
The system shall present me with a search button

Given I have opened the ebay website
The system shall present me a search field

Given I have opened the ebay website
When I select to Register
The system shall present me with a first name, surname, email and password field

Given I have opened the ebay website
When I select to Register
The system shall present me with an "email or username" field

Given I have opened the ebay website
When I input text into the search box
And select to search
The system shall present me with a list of items related to my search
